  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Viking trash compactor service? Same-day across LA:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Viking › Trash Compactor Repair</div>
    <h1>Viking Trash Compactor Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Viking is one of three brands still producing residential trash compactors in the US — the luxury built-in category that most mass-market manufacturers exited 2009-2015. Viking VGCC and VTCP 15-inch built-in trash compactors ship into LA luxury kitchens as part of a coordinated Viking pro-range suite, with 1.4 cubic foot compaction chamber, pro-grade drive train, and stainless-steel door-panel integration matched to the broader Viking Professional 7 Series aesthetic. Middleby Corporation owns Viking since 2002; the Greenwood MS factory has manufactured continuously since the brand's 1987 founding. Parts distribution via Middleby runs 4-6 day typical lead on common service components to LA-authorized service. Our LA Viking service covers Bel Air + Beverly Hills + Pacific Palisades + Malibu + Manhattan Beach + Pasadena luxury built-in kitchen installs across both current-production VGCC / VTCP units and legacy Viking trash compactor platforms back through the 1990s. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
